The paper deals with image description and narrative generation, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. The paper also proposes a customized approach to generate descriptions based on user interests, which involves machine learning techniques such as reinforcement learning (cs.AI), deep learning (cs.LG), and information retrieval (cs.IR).
